article.description: — Darius McGhee had a career-high 34 points as Liberty stretched its winning streak to nine games and captured the Atlantic Sun Conference regular season championship with a 94-78...
article.headline: McGhee scores 34, Liberty tops Bellarmine to win A-Sun
article.linkText: McGhee scores 34, Liberty tops Bellarmine to win A-Sun
article.story: LOUISVILLE, Ky. -- — Darius McGhee had a career-high 34 points as Liberty stretched its winning streak to nine games and captured the Atlantic Sun Conference regular season championship with a 94-78 win over Bellarmine on Saturday. McGhee shot 8 for 11 on 3-pointers. Chris Parker had 19 points for Liberty (20-5, 11-2). Elijah Cuffee added 12 points. Shiloh Robinson had 11 points and nine rebounds. Pedro Bradshaw had 20 points and four steals for the Knights (13-6, 10-3), whose 10-game winning streak came to an end. Dylan Penn added 17 points. CJ Fleming had 16 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
